P210: Keep away from heat, sparks, open flames and hot surfaces. - No smoking. P211: Do not spray on an open flame or other ignition source. P251: Pressurized container: Do not pierce or burn, even after use. P261: Avoid breathing fumes, mists, vapours or spray. P301+P330+P331: IF SWALLOWED: Rinse mouth. Do NOT induce vomiting., EXTREMELY FLAMMABLE. DO NOT SPRAY ON A NAKED FLAME OR INCANDESCENT MATERIAL.
